description: Great investment opportunity for homeowners, investors, or builders! This semi-attached townhouse-style single family offers 2BRs and over 1,000 sq ft across 2 floors. Features include an indoor porch, fenced private yard, and a walk-out basement – ideal for storage or potential to expand living space. Located just one block from East & West Broadway, enjoy unbeatable access to grocery stores, shops, restaurants, and public transit. A commuter’s dream close to downtown & Seaport. Endless potential in a prime South Boston location! OPEN HOUSE - Wednesday, July 16th - 5 to 6:30pm and Saturday, July 19th - 12 to 1:30pm
